If you modify the query to select the state and
        city from the `travel-sample` bucket using the same
      index idx_state, the index does not contain the values of the
        city field to satisfy the query, and hence a key-value fetch is
      performed to retrieve this data.
      EXPLAIN SELECT state,city FROM `travel-sample` USE INDEX (idx_state) WHERE type="hotel" AND state = "CA";

